headline: Browning West LP publishes letter to the Board of Domino's Pizza Group PLC
summary: Browning West, LP ("Browning West"), one of the largest shareholders of Domino's Pizza Group PLC ("Domino's" or "the Company"), with an approximate 5% stake, is today publishing a letter sent to the Company's Board of Directors on 7 August 2025, prior to the Company's announcement on 1 September 2025 of a £20 million share buyback programme.
